  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下新的数据平台架构。目前有三个数据源：外部API、遗留数据库，还有一个事件流。我想先确认这些入口怎么统一处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "DB",
        "Stream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。外部API和遗留数据库的数据特性比较接近，都是批量的；事件流是实时的。我们是不是该用不同的摄取方式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "DB",
        "Stream",
        "Glue",
        "Lambda"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，批量走AWS Glue做ETL，实时流用Lambda处理。这两个都落到同一个存储层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Glue",
        "Lambda",
        "S3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我把摄取层画出来：Glue负责API和DB，Lambda对接事件流，输出都指向S3数据湖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Glue",
        "Lambda",
        "S3",
        "API",
        "DB",
        "Stream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "S3之后需要分流处理。批量数据走Spark做转换，实时流要单独一个流处理器。这两个最终都要进Snowflake。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S3",
        "Spark",
        "Stream2",
        "Snowflake"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Spark Jobs是批处理，Stream Processor是实时处理，两者并行从S3取数据，然后都写入Snowflake？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Spark",
        "Stream2",
        "S3",
        "Snowflake"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。Snowflake作为统一的数据仓库层，上面再挂消费端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Snowflake"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "处理层和消费层都加上了。Snowflake下游我放了BI仪表盘、数据API和ML模型三个出口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Snowflake",
        "BI",
        "API2",
        "ML"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "数据API这块，命名会不会和前面的External APIs混淆？需要区分一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "API2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确实，我标注成Data APIs，和入口的External APIs区分开。入口是第三方数据进来，出口是我们对外暴露的数据服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "API2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "整体结构差不多了，但视觉上需要突出核心组件。S3作为数据湖、Snowflake作为仓库、还有Spark，这三个是枢纽，用颜色标出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S3",
        "Snowflake",
        "Spark"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "S3用AWS橙色，Snowflake用品牌蓝，Spark也用它的标志性橙色。这样一眼就能看到关键节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S3",
        "Snowflake",
        "Spark"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
