      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Spark我调深一点到E25A1C，S3保持FF9900，区别还是有的。Snowflake用29B5E8配白字，可读性没问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S3",
