      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Stream Processor我标注成Stream2，和入口的Event Stream区分。这个命名可以接受吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Stream",
        "Stream2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，Stream2代表处理后的流处理组件。所有连线方向再检查一遍，确保是从左到右的单向流动。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Stream2"
