    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "链路确认：API→Glue→S3→Spark→Snowflake→BI/API2/ML，DB并行走Glue，Stream→Lambda→S3→Stream2→Snowflake。没有回流。",
